   March 5, 2002 Primary Election

   Live Election Returns 2002 Primary Election - Voter Information Guide
   On-line Voter Registration Card [spacer.gif]

                                Vote America

                               IMPORTANT DATES
                              FOR MARCH 5, 2002
                              PRIMARY ELECTION

     * Registration Deadline -
       2/19/02
     * First day to apply for an absentee ballot BY MAIL - 2/4/02
     * Last day to apply for an absentee ballot BY MAIL - 2/26/02
     * Last day to apply for an absentee ballot IN PERSON at the office of
       the County Election official - 3/05/02
     * Election Day - 3/05/02
       Polls are open from
       7 a.m. to 8 p.m.
       (All absentee ballots need to be receieved by election officials by
       the close of the polls at
       8 p.m.)
     * Late Contribution/Late Independent Expenditure Reporting - 2/17/02
       - 3/04/02

